flowchart TB
  %% Diagram 38: PostgreSQL RLS Isolation and Cross-Vendor Privacy Flow

  Req[Authenticated query request]
  Ctx[Attach actor_id and tenant_id to DB session]
  QueryType{Query type}

  VendorRead[Vendor scoped table query]
  BuyerRead[Buyer order history query]
  AggregateRead[Cross-vendor analytics query]

  RLS{RLS policy condition passes?}
  OwnRows[Return tenant-scoped rows only]
  Denied[Block cross-tenant access]

  AggCheck{vendor_count >= 3 and aggregate-only fields?}
  AggOK[Return privacy-safe aggregate analytics]
  AggBlock[Suppress result and return policy notice]

  Req --> Ctx --> QueryType
  QueryType -- Vendor --> VendorRead --> RLS
  QueryType -- Buyer --> BuyerRead --> RLS
  QueryType -- Aggregate --> AggregateRead --> AggCheck

  RLS -- Yes --> OwnRows
  RLS -- No --> Denied

  AggCheck -- Yes --> AggOK
  AggCheck -- No --> AggBlock
